<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RNA-seq 差异表达分析报告</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #2c3e50;
      --accent: #3498db;
      --success: #27ae60;
      --warning: #f39c12;
      --danger: #e74c3c;
      --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
      --border: #dee2e6;
      --text: #2c3e50;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }

    /* Header */
    .report-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #34495e);
      color: white; padding: 40px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .report-header h1 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .report-header p { opacity: 0.85; font-size: 14px; }

    /* Navigation */
    .toc {
      background: var(--light-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .toc h3 { color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; }
    .toc ol { padding-left: 20px; }
    .toc li { margin: 4px 0; }
    .toc a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    .toc a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Sections */
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 40px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .section-header {
      background: var(--primary); color: white;
      padding: 15px 20px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .section-content { padding: 24px; }

    /* Subsections */
    .subsection { margin: 20px 0; }
    .subsection h3 {
      color: var(--primary); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-bottom: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .subsection h4 { color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 6px; }

    /* Cards */
    .card {
      background: var(--light-bg); border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px; margin: 12px 0; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }
    .card.warning { border-left-color: var(--warning); }
    .card.danger  { border-left-color: var(--danger); }
    .card.success { border-left-color: var(--success); }

    /* Stats grid */
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .stat-box {
      background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-box .value { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); }
    .stat-box .label { font-size: 11px; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* Badges */
    .badge {
      display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; margin: 2px;
    }
    .badge-primary  { background: #d6e4ff; color: #1a56db; }
    .badge-success  { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
    .badge-warning  { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .badge-danger   { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
    .badge-secondary{ background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; }

    /* Plots */
    .plot-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(360px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .plot-item { text-align: center; }
    .plot-item img { max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; }
    .plot-caption { font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 6px; font-style: italic; }
    .plot-missing {
      background: #f9f9f9; border: 2px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px; padding: 40px; text-align: center;
      color: #999; font-size: 13px;
    }

    /* Tables */
    .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; margin: 12px 0; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
    th { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; text-align: left; }
    td { padding: 7px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--light-bg); }
    tr:hover { background: #e8f4fd; }

    /* Narrative text */
    .narrative { line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text); }
    .narrative p { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    /* Contrast tabs */
    .contrast-section { margin: 20px 0; }
    .contrast-header {
      background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 12px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }

    /* Findings list */
    .findings-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .findings-list li {
      padding: 10px 14px; margin: 6px 0; border-radius: 6px;
      border-left: 4px solid;
    }
    .finding-high   { background: #fff0f0; border-color: var(--danger); }
    .finding-medium { background: #fffbf0; border-color: var(--warning); }
    .finding-low    { background: #f0fff4; border-color: var(--success); }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #888;
      font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 40px;
    }

    /* Collapsible */
    details { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; margin: 8px 0; }
    summary { padding: 10px 14px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500; background: var(--light-bg); }
    summary:hover { background: #e9ecef; }
    details[open] summary { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .details-content { padding: 14px; }

    @media print {
      .toc { display: none; }
      .section { break-inside: avoid; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="report-header">
    <h1>RNA-seq 差异表达分析报告</h1>
    <p>物种: {{ species }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; 对比组数: {{ contrasts | length }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; 由 DESeq2Agent 自动生成</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Table of Contents -->
  <div class="toc">
    <h3>目录</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><a href="#executive-summary">执行摘要</a></li>
      <li><a href="#methods">分析方法</a></li>
      <li><a href="#qc">质量控制评估</a></li>
      <li><a href="#de">差异表达分析</a>
        <ol>
          {% for ct in contrasts %}
          <li><a href="#de-{{ ct.name }}">{{ ct.name }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#enrichment">通路富集分析</a>
        <ol>
          {% for ct in contrasts %}
          <li><a href="#enrich-{{ ct.name }}">{{ ct.name }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#key-findings">关键发现</a></li>
      <li><a href="#conclusions">结论与局限性</a></li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <!-- 1. Executive Summary -->
  <div class="section" id="executive-summary">
    <div class="section-header">1. 执行摘要</div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="card success">
        <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.executive_summary }}</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick stats -->
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="value">{{ qc_metrics.n_samples | default('N/A') }}</div>
          <div class="label">样本总数</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="value">{{ qc_metrics.n_genes_filtered | default('N/A') }}</div>
          <div class="label">分析基因数</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="value">{{ contrasts | length }}</div>
          <div class="label">对比组数</div>
        </div>
        {% if qc_decision.samples_to_remove %}
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="value" style="color: var(--warning)">{{ qc_decision.samples_to_remove | length }}</div>
          <div class="label">移除样本数</div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% for ct_name, ct_data in de_summary.items() %}
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="value">{{ (ct_data.n_sig_up | default(0)) + (ct_data.n_sig_down | default(0)) }}</div>
          <div class="label">{{ ct_name }} 差异基因</div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. Methods -->
  <div class="section" id="methods">
    <div class="section-header">2. 分析方法</div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.methods_paragraph }}</div>
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>对比组设计</h3>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>对比名称</th><th>变量</th><th>处理组</th><th>对照组</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
            {% for ct in contrasts %}
            <tr>
              <td><strong>{{ ct.name }}</strong></td>
              <td>{{ ct.variable }}</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-danger">{{ ct.treatment }}</span></td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-secondary">{{ ct.control }}</span></td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. QC -->
  <div class="section" id="qc">
    <div class="section-header">3. 质量控制评估</div>
    <div class="section-content">

      <!-- QC Status -->
      {% set usability_class = {'proceed': 'success', 'proceed_with_caution': 'warning', 'stop': 'danger'} %}
      <div class="card {{ usability_class.get(qc_decision.data_usability, '') }}">
        <strong>数据可用性:</strong>
        {% if qc_decision.data_usability == 'proceed' %}
          <span class="badge badge-success">正常推进</span>
        {% elif qc_decision.data_usability == 'proceed_with_caution' %}
          <span class="badge badge-warning">谨慎推进</span>
        {% else %}
          <span class="badge badge-danger">建议停止</span>
        {% endif %}
        &nbsp; <strong>批次效应:</strong>
        <span class="badge badge-{{ 'danger' if qc_decision.batch_effect_present else 'success' }}">
          {{ qc_decision.batch_effect_severity }}
        </span>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">{{ qc_decision.quality_summary }}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- QC Flags -->
      {% if qc_decision.qc_flags %}
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>QC 警告</h3>
        {% for flag in qc_decision.qc_flags %}
        <div class="card warning" style="padding:8px 14px; margin:4px 0">⚠ {{ flag }}</div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- Outlier samples -->
      {% if qc_decision.outlier_samples %}
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>潜在离群样本</h3>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>样本</th><th>原因</th><th>置信度</th><th>处理</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
            {% for s in qc_decision.outlier_samples %}
            <tr>
              <td><strong>{{ s.sample_id }}</strong></td>
              <td>{{ s.reason }}</td>
              <td>
                <span class="badge {{ 'badge-danger' if s.confidence == 'high' else ('badge-warning' if s.confidence == 'medium' else 'badge-secondary') }}">
                  {{ s.confidence }}
                </span>
              </td>
              <td>
                {% if s.sample_id in qc_decision.samples_to_remove %}
                  <span class="badge badge-danger">已移除</span>
                {% else %}
                  <span class="badge badge-success">保留</span>
                {% endif %}
              </td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- QC Narrative -->
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>QC 分析叙述</h3>
        <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.qc_narrative }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
        <strong>PCA 解读:</strong> {{ qc_decision.pca_interpretation }}
      </div>

      <!-- QC Plots -->
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>QC 图表</h3>
        <div class="plot-grid">
          {% set plot_labels = {'pca': 'PCA 图', 'heatmap': '样本相关性热图', 'mds': 'MDS 图',
                                'dispersion': '离散度估计', 'library_sizes': '文库大小',
                                'detected_genes': '检测基因数'} %}
          {% for plot_name, label in plot_labels.items() %}
          <div class="plot-item">
            {% if qc_plot_data.get(plot_name) %}
              <img src="{{ qc_plot_data[plot_name] }}" alt="{{ label }}">
            {% else %}
              <div class="plot-missing">{{ label }}<br><small>图像不可用</small></div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="plot-caption">图: {{ label }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. Differential Expression -->
  <div class="section" id="de">
    <div class="section-header">4. 差异表达分析</div>
    <div class="section-content">

      <div class="subsection">
        <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.de_narrative }}</div>
      </div>

      {% for ct in contrasts %}
      {% set ct_name = ct.name %}
      {% set ct_data = de_summary.get(ct_name, {}) %}
      <div class="contrast-section" id="de-{{ ct_name }}">
        <div class="contrast-header">
          {{ ct_name }}: {{ ct.treatment }} vs {{ ct.control }}
          &nbsp;
          <span class="badge badge-danger">↑ {{ ct_data.get('n_sig_up', 0) }} 上调</span>
          <span class="badge badge-primary">↓ {{ ct_data.get('n_sig_down', 0) }} 下调</span>
          <span class="badge badge-secondary">共检验 {{ ct_data.get('n_total_tested', 'N/A') }} 基因</span>
        </div>

        <!-- DE Plots -->
        <div class="plot-grid">
          {% if de_plot_data.get(ct_name, {}).get('volcano') %}
          <div class="plot-item">
            <img src="{{ de_plot_data[ct_name]['volcano'] }}" alt="Volcano Plot">
            <div class="plot-caption">火山图: {{ ct_name }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if de_plot_data.get(ct_name, {}).get('ma') %}
          <div class="plot-item">
            <img src="{{ de_plot_data[ct_name]['ma'] }}" alt="MA Plot">
            <div class="plot-caption">MA 图: {{ ct_name }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- Top genes tables -->
        <details>
          <summary>Top 上调基因 (前20名)</summary>
          <div class="details-content">
            {% if ct_data.get('top20_up_genes') %}
            <div class="table-wrap">
              <table>
                <thead><tr><th>Gene ID</th><th>Symbol</th><th>log2FC</th><th>padj</th></tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for g in ct_data.top20_up_genes %}
                <tr>
                  <td>{{ g.gene_id | default('') }}</td>
                  <td><strong>{{ g.symbol | default('') }}</strong></td>
                  <td style="color:var(--danger)">{{ "%.3f" | format(g.log2FoldChange | float) if g.log2FoldChange is defined else 'N/A' }}</td>
                  <td>{{ "%.2e" | format(g.padj | float) if g.padj is defined else 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <p style="color:#888">无显著上调基因</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>Top 下调基因 (前20名)</summary>
          <div class="details-content">
            {% if ct_data.get('top20_down_genes') %}
            <div class="table-wrap">
              <table>
                <thead><tr><th>Gene ID</th><th>Symbol</th><th>log2FC</th><th>padj</th></tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for g in ct_data.top20_down_genes %}
                <tr>
                  <td>{{ g.gene_id | default('') }}</td>
                  <td><strong>{{ g.symbol | default('') }}</strong></td>
                  <td style="color:var(--accent)">{{ "%.3f" | format(g.log2FoldChange | float) if g.log2FoldChange is defined else 'N/A' }}</td>
                  <td>{{ "%.2e" | format(g.padj | float) if g.padj is defined else 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <p style="color:#888">无显著下调基因</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. Enrichment Analysis -->
  <div class="section" id="enrichment">
    <div class="section-header">5. 通路富集分析</div>
    <div class="section-content">

      <div class="subsection">
        <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.pathway_narrative }}</div>
      </div>

      {% for ct in contrasts %}
      {% set ct_name = ct.name %}
      {% set enrich = enrichment_by_contrast.get(ct_name, {}) %}
      <div class="contrast-section" id="enrich-{{ ct_name }}">
        <div class="contrast-header">
          {{ ct_name }} 富集结果
          {% if enrich.get('ora_skipped') %}
          <span class="badge badge-warning">ORA 已跳过 (显著基因 &lt; 10)</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- Enrichment Plots -->
        {% set enrich_plots = enrich_plot_data.get(ct_name, {}) %}
        {% if enrich_plots %}
        <div class="plot-grid">
          {% set enrich_plot_labels = {
            'gsea_go_dotplot': 'GSEA GO 点图',
            'gsea_kegg_dotplot': 'GSEA KEGG 点图',
            'ora_go_dotplot': 'ORA GO 点图',
            'ora_kegg_dotplot': 'ORA KEGG 点图'
          } %}
          {% for pname, plabel in enrich_plot_labels.items() %}
          {% if enrich_plots.get(pname) %}
          <div class="plot-item">
            <img src="{{ enrich_plots[pname] }}" alt="{{ plabel }}">
            <div class="plot-caption">{{ plabel }}: {{ ct_name }}</div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Top pathways table -->
        {% for analysis_type in ['gsea_go', 'gsea_kegg', 'ora_go', 'ora_kegg'] %}
        {% set rows = enrich.get(analysis_type) %}
        {% if rows %}
        <details>
          <summary>{{ analysis_type | upper }} Top 通路</summary>
          <div class="details-content">
            <div class="table-wrap">
              <table>
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>ID</th>
                    <th>描述</th>
                    {% if analysis_type.startswith('gsea') %}<th>NES</th>{% endif %}
                    <th>p.adjust</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for row in rows[:15] %}
                <tr>
                  <td>{{ row.get('ID', '') }}</td>
                  <td>{{ row.get('Description', '') }}</td>
                  {% if analysis_type.startswith('gsea') %}
                  <td>
                    {% set nes = row.get('NES', 0) | float %}
                    <span style="color: {{ 'var(--danger)' if nes > 0 else 'var(--accent)' }}">
                      {{ "%.3f" | format(nes) }}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                  {% endif %}
                  <td>{{ "%.3e" | format(row.get('p.adjust', 1) | float) }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}

      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. Key Findings -->
  <div class="section" id="key-findings">
    <div class="section-header">6. 关键发现</div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <ul class="findings-list">
        {% for f in narrative.key_findings %}
        <li class="finding-{{ f.get('priority', 'low') }}">
          <span class="badge {{ 'badge-danger' if f.priority == 'high' else ('badge-warning' if f.priority == 'medium' else 'badge-success') }}">
            {{ f.get('priority', 'low').upper() }}
          </span>
          &nbsp; {{ f.get('finding', '') }}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 7. Conclusions and Limitations -->
  <div class="section" id="conclusions">
    <div class="section-header">7. 结论与局限性</div>
    <div class="section-content">

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>结论</h3>
        <div class="narrative">{{ narrative.conclusions }}</div>
      </div>

      {% if narrative.limitations %}
      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>局限性</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2">
          {% for lim in narrative.limitations %}
          <li>{{ lim }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>本报告由 <strong>DESeq2Agent</strong> 自动生成 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 分析引擎: DESeq2 + clusterProfiler + LangChain LLM</p>
    <p style="margin-top:4px; color:#aaa">结果仅供参考，请结合实验背景和专业知识进行解读</p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
